title: FREE SPEED TEST - Test your download and upload speed
description:
These files can be used to test your uploading/downloading over your LAN or the Internet.

The SPEED_TEST.zip file contains the following files:

1_GB_TEST.bin	A 1 GB file filled with the NULL character
10_GB_TEST.bin	A 10 GB file filled with the NULL character
100_MB_TEST.bin	A 100 MB file filled with the NULL character
SPEED_TEST.txt	This file that you are now reading

These files can be transferred fast when using protocol compression schemes.
